"display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.marxists.org/reference/archive/einstein/works/1910s/relative/ch18.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.marxists.org/reference/archive/einstein/works/1910s/relative/ch18.htm" rel="nofollow">Albert Einstein, Relativity - The Special and General Theory, chapter 18</a></li>
