<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLev_B._Okun1989">Lev B. Okun (July 1989), "<a href="http://www.physicstoday.org/vol-42/iss-6/vol42no6p31_36.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.physicstoday.org/vol-42/iss-6/vol42no6p31_36.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Concept of Mass</a>" (subscription required), <i>Physics Today</i> <b>42</b> (6): 31–36, <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1063%2F1.881171" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1063%2F1.881171" rel="nofollow">10.1063/1.881171</a></span><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.physicstoday.org/vol-42/iss-6/vol42no6p31_36.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.physicstoday.org/vol-42/iss-6/vol42no6p31_36.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.physicstoday.org/vol-42/iss-6/vol42no6p31_36.pdf</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Concept+of+Mass&amp;rft.jtitle=Physics+Today&amp;rft.aulast=Lev+B.+Okun&amp;rft.au=Lev+B.+Okun&amp;rft.date=July+1989&amp;rft.volume=42&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=31%E2%80%9336&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1063%2F1.881171&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.physicstoday.org%2Fvol-42%2Fiss-6%2Fvol42no6p31_36.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Special_relativity"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFT._R._Sandin1991">T. R. Sandin (November 1991), "<a href="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=AJPIAS000059000011001032000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" class="external text" title="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=AJPIAS000059000011001032000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" rel="nofollow">In defense of relativistic mass</a>" (subscription required), <i>American Journal of Physics</i> <b>59</b> (11): 1032, <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1119%2F1.16642" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1119%2F1.16642" rel="nofollow">10.1119/1.16642</a></span><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=AJPIAS000059000011001032000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" class="external free" title="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=AJPIAS000059000011001032000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" rel="nofollow">http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=AJPIAS000059000011001032000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=In+defense+of+relativistic+mass&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Physics&amp;rft.aulast=T.+R.+Sandin&amp;rft.au=T.+R.+Sandin&amp;rft.date=November+1991&amp;rft.volume=59&amp;rft.issue=11&amp;rft.pages=1032&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1119%2F1.16642&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fscitation.aip.org%2Fgetabs%2Fservlet%2FGetabsServlet%3Fprog%3Dnormal%26id%3DAJPIAS000059000011001032000001%26idtype%3Dcvips%26gifs%3Dyes&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Special_relativity"><span style="display: no