<li><a href="/wiki/Robert_Geroch" title="Robert Geroch">Robert Geroch</a> (1981). <i>General Relativity From A to B</i>. University of Chicago Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0226288641" class="internal">ISBN 0-226-28864-1</a></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGr.C3.B8nHervik.2C_Sigbj.C3.B8rn2007">Grøn, Øyvind; Hervik, Sigbjørn (2007). <i>Einstein's General Theory of Relativity</i>. New York: Springer. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780387691992" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-387-69199-2</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Einstein%27s+General+Theory+of+Relativity&amp;rft.aulast=Gr%C3%B8n&amp;rft.aufirst=%C3%98yvind&amp;rft.au=Gr%C3%B8n%2C+%C3%98yvind&amp;rft.au=Hervik%2C+Sigbj%C3%B8rn&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Springer&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-387-69199-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Special_relativity"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
